        "created_at": "2017-04-16T04:09:55.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Typo, I\u2019m sure you meant Pothier-Rieusset. I\u2019ve had their '85 Pommard Rugiens. Very nice. When Virgil Pothier-Rieusset\u2019s niece, Marianne, married Laurent Pillot, she brought with her half of the P-R estate to Domaine Pillot. By 2001, Pillot had purchased the rest.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/8/0/80db0489d091cb083d575a0b95a424444015af3c.jpeg\" alt=\"image.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"inUmi3l5NCQrCfN6HTYEhkRyjF2\" width=\"336\" height=\"448\"></p>",
