        "created_at": "2017-04-16T04:15:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"LMD Ermita\u00f1o\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n LMD Ermita\u00f1o:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Typo, I\u2019m sure you meant Pothier-Rieusset. I\u2019ve had their '85 Pommard Rugiens. Very nice. When Virgil Pothier-Rieusset\u2019s niece, Marianne, married Laurent Pillot, she brought with her half of the P-R estate to Domaine Pillot. By 2001, Pillot had purchased the rest.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You\u2019re right. Not a typo, I just read the label wrong. Quite a bizarre looking \u201cP\u201d.</p>",
